ActTerritorial Lands Act
PrecisWITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (EDÉHZHÍE [HORN PLATEAU]) ORDER - which withdraws from disposal some 2,458,972 hectares of territory situated in an area known as Edéhzhíe (Horn Plateau) until October 31, 2010, in order to facilitate the establishment of a National Wildlife Area.
